      <h1 class="pb-4">About</h1>
      <p>
        Tours and trips, whether they're family vacations, business trips, or road trips, are always exhilarating and a
        fantastic way to relax. Properly managing your journey is crucial. Have you ever been on a trip where you spent
        more time traveling than sightseeing? That sounds like a nightmare! But don't worry, we have the solution for
        you!
      </p>
      <p>
        "TravelSmart" is a platform where you can find optimal routes for various trip types. We offer you the
        choice to optimize routes by either distance or time. But that's not all. You also receive route recommendations
        tailored to your chosen mode of transport. Plus, you can choose between two types of journeys: round trips
        (where the starting and ending locations are the same) or one-way trips.
      </p>
      <p>
        Importantly, "TravelSmart" is more than just a tour planning platform. Beyond personal trips, it can also
        assist with heavy luggage transportation via trucks and similar vehicles, where optimizing costs (and
        consequently distance) is paramount. Travel agencies and bus companies can leverage our platform to minimize
        travel expenses. Whether for road trips, walking excursions, or other needs, our tool is versatile and always at
        your service. If you need assistance, check the "How to Use" section.
      </p>


